Use the following nuget packages and frameworks for this project:
    - MediatR for implementing CQRS
    - xUnit for testing
    - NSubstitute for creating fake implementations of interfaces in unit tests
    - Verify when needed to assert the correct state of more than 5 properties
    - BootstrapBlazor for UI
    - EF Core and SQLite for database access, using code-first migrations.